Patent Non-Assert
-----------------
To promote open implementations, each contributor to the AIR
specification and its schemas grants a perpetual, worldwide,
royalty-free, non-exclusive license to any patent claims that are
necessarily infringed by implementing the normative portions of
these specifications.

This patent license applies only to implementations of the AIR
specification as defined here; it does not grant rights for any
other use of a contributorâ€™s patents.

If a contributor initiates or participates in a claim alleging that
an implementation of this specification infringes a patent it owns
